31 dollars ($1,623,510) in recurring funds beginning in the 2025-2026 fiscal year and thirty-seven
32 thousand five hundred twenty dollars ($37,520) in nonrecurring funds in the 2025-2026 fiscal
33 year to be used to hire 10 full-time assistant district attorneys in Prosecutorial District 26,
